/X/     - match operator
m/X/    - generalized match operator
m?X?    - generalized match operator
s/X/Y/  - substitution operator
tr/X/Y/ - transliteration operator
y/X/Y/  - transliteration operator
<<`X`   - backtick heredoc operator
~~      - smartmatch (currently documented, but poorly)
qx      - doesn't interpolate if delimiter is '
qr      - doesn't interpolate if delimiter is '

